data.description: MAKE AN OFFER!  Country charmer on acreage. This lovingly maintained home is perfect. Are you looking for your 1st home or to add to your investment portfolio?  Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, central to town, and within just a few blocks from highway 33 your morning commute would be a breeze.  The fenced in back yard is a nice touch with gorgeous mature trees for shade.  Enjoy nights overlooking your property and watching the deer and wildlife frequent the backside of the property. This property offers an awesome shop with concrete floors, electric throughout, outbuildings, and 4 bedrooms!  There is also ample opportunity to add an additional bathroom.  Call now to come take a look.
